('Which stat would you like to measure?', 'Which stat would you like to measure?', 309753, 0, 0, 0, 256, 0, 4, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 67186),
('I have lost enough of my own kin at the hands of the Silver Covenant. \n\nIt was war, they tell me. Both sides took losses, they say. My Sunreavers never purged anyone from Dalaran. \n\nOne Windrunner met her justice for purging a city. The other faces me today.', '', 289969, 0, 0, 0, 256, 0, 4, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 67186);
