(3341, 'Veteran Dawncrest', 'Used to upgrade Veteran equipment in Midnight Season 1 up to item levels 237-250.  \n\nWhen used for crafting, sets the item level of the resulting item to 233-246 based on Quality.\n\nEarned from the following activities:\n\n- Repeatable Outdoor Events\n- Raid Finder Voidspire, The Dreamrift, March On Quel\'Danas\n- Heroic Season Dungeons\n- Delves (Tiers 5 to 6)\n- Trovehunter\'s Bounty (Tiers 4 to 5)\n- Prey Hunts (Hard)', 268, 7639525, 0, 0, 100, 0, 4, 0, 0, 0, 142396, 29184, 0, 0, 0, 2, 0, 0, 5, 35913922, 1, 67186),
